OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fcloudy through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with further outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain, turning heavy at times and
OL,9,Fperhaps quite persistent for Orkney
OL,10,Flater. Some haar patches around.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FLargely cloudy throughout the
OL,13,Fday with some haar and outbreaks of
OL,14,Frain, occasionally heavy and perhaps
OL,15,Fquite persistent for a time in the
OL,16,Fmorning. Becoming generally drier and
OL,17,Fbrighter later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
