OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry on Monday with some bright spells
OL,7,Fbetween areas of low cloud. Cloudy on
OL,8,FTuesday and Wednesday with occasional
OL,9,Frain. Mainly light winds. Areas of
OL,10,Fhaar at times.
